{"title":"AMBOSS Reacción Transfusional-2025","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/AMBOSS Reacción Transfusional-2025.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Reacción\\NTransfusional","guid":"mTpP8Wsk3y1bZygecJ-Gpw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"## Resumen","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- Las transfusiones de componentes sanguíneos son generalmente seguras","guid":"ZqJlD3KgMndixySXZwXpaw","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"- Los eventos adversos graves son poco comunes gracias a extensos exámenes previos","guid":"k2mU95ZpChkuGDR7kdqktg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"- Las reacciones agudas suelen ser leves (fiebre y erupción)","guid":"yvSuzgtaaPO-c53DCWCjMQ","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"- Raramente ocurren reacciones graves (dificultad respiratoria, hemólisis, shock)","guid":"kLecehKAqQ-5rDPx0yQcsQ","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"- Ante cualquier reacción, se debe detener la transfusión y realizar evaluación","guid":"VhJa01Z72lC3wcAfxVKacA","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"- Las reacciones tardías pueden presentarse días/semanas después de la transfusión","guid":"AL8DwNVbhSSIwVMxadc85Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"## Reacciones Transfusionales\\NInmunológicas","guid":"-adXnHrIMYYDIOV0B5qxoQ","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"### Reacción Hemolítica\\NTransfusional Aguda\\N(AHTR)","guid":"CKYhlsgkm9NHgHG-Pk4FWQ","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"- **Frecuencia**: 1:105, 000-200,000 transfusiones","guid":"agaMFpCf0WZiJnnnzmIsAQ","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"- **Mecanismo**: Destrucción de eritrocitos por anticuerpos preformados del receptor","guid":"uUCCQT5JWPY0zMhE8miLJQ","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"- **Inicio**: Durante o hasta 24h post-transfusión","guid":"UaM8uBuAGTWF-zaJRWfKGw","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"9","text":"- **Manifestaciones**:","guid":"XpXENGxmCNDJSf-rzkKngA","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"- Fiebre, escalofríos, náuseas, rubor","guid":"teYoJjUra1Y3AjqjoMp4YA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"- Signos de shock","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"- Signos de dificultad respiratoria","guid":"WwG3ebcphUVmvpMjQDX_jg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"13","text":"- Signos de hemólisis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"9","text":"- **Manejo**:","guid":"k5Qm1DTDRhK8bkRCxYGrhw","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"- Detener inmediatamente la transfusión","guid":"P2ql7gdq7agRYm8xqrT2Qw","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"- Notificar al banco de sangre","guid":"Z2hgAMA1wV-3jR500Ag05A","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"- Test de Coombs directo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"18","text":"- Soporte hemodinámico inmediato","guid":"Mi_tQ7C2DGOToFoWeqOHBQ","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"18","text":"- Tratamiento de complicaciones (hiperpotasemia, CID, fallo renal)","guid":"wr2k3I7ApsPV1xRka5uiNw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"8","text":"### Reacción Febril No\\NHemolítica (FNHTR)","guid":"8_a-BCOGu7JkZv7Dm6jd3g","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"- **Frecuencia**: 1:900 transfusiones (más común en niños)","guid":"Be99e8zTvR50yggPq3S6hA","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"- **Mecanismo**: Citoquinas liberadas de leucocitos del donante","guid":"KhbCpoAgTtwGDKLpw9Px5w","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"- **Inicio**: Durante o hasta 6h post-transfusión","guid":"XiDW0Ta6DjCRIR0zDF8rAg","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"24","text":"- **Manifestaciones**: Fiebre, escalofríos, malestar, rubor, cefalea","guid":"4jMXHNxhbcYqUSXz-g8W6g","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"24","text":"- **Manejo**:","guid":"BAf1FGsYwE9-em_MGgQLvA","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"- Detener transfusión hasta descartar AHTR","guid":"LBcgt99rjhbfdhujqfjhag","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"- Productos leucorreducidos para prevención","guid":"YYH4hmVvw5cRFSoFpZ6IBQ","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"- Acetaminofén para síntomas","guid":"uvEDPQgnCwrr5Y2g79BxFw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"8","text":"### Reacción\\NAnafiláctica\\NTransfusional","guid":"-TQ7Ngc_4L6u7FNtyhXWqg","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"- **Frecuencia**: 1:30, 000 transfusiones","guid":"Q5rMvNqm3ILWuM0FBDRDaQ","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"- **Mecanismo**: Hipersensibilidad tipo I a proteínas plasmáticas del donante","guid":"bqWz_xu7EEHtFcmaeulZGw","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"- **Inicio**: Súbito; durante o hasta 3h post-transfusión","guid":"wdX-0p8dE5SlH8cqhmHe_g","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"- **Manifestaciones**: Características clínicas de anafilaxia","guid":"gx863eu7Ok-2yO-sZQPc4A","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"33","text":"- **Manejo**:","guid":"s0nx58RV0oBTa65Xlr2ZQA","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"- Detener inmediatamente la transfusión","guid":"HAz3Uq_MVPMTYeoH25_B4A","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"- Epinefrina IM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"- Soporte hemodinámico inmediato","guid":"H81e8_LiPAVwM2mqq5nUvA","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"38","text":"- Manejo de vía aérea","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"8","text":"### Reacción\\NAlérgica Menor","guid":"m8fS8Qlfsts8eR8CYid6lg","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"- **Frecuencia**: 1:1,200 transfusiones (más común en niños)","guid":"vaYV8Tcop0aFgRYHVcdkUA","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"- **Mecanismo**: Reacción alérgica a componentes del plasma del donante","guid":"bV2k6S333nZF-WkUhbu6RA","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"- **Inicio**: Durante o hasta 4h post-transfusión","guid":"Y0s-iZc3hPiIRSif75MiPA","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"43","text":"- **Manifestaciones**: Prurito, urticaria","guid":"QJfPOiiA4yKh3BkMwB5_tw","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"43","text":"- **Manejo**:","guid":"otKJYghMIKUOVIj3aGRTVQ","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"- Detener transfusión inicialmente","guid":"VBcOtxGM7Hr_hQ8mevsRRw","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"- Difenhidramina para síntomas","guid":"MSyD234bIe0vOzGzpcvE5Q","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"- Reiniciar lentamente bajo observación si se descarta anafilaxia","guid":"INrbXPBnn_uGNZpJuXU39A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"8","text":"### Lesión Pulmonar Aguda\\NRelacionada con Transfusión\\N(TRALI)","guid":"k_dwMV9zkbamfid9BvBXsQ","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"- **Frecuencia**: 1:60, 000 transfusiones","guid":"CLlZzNdVlPaJ7HaMLQei5g","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"- **Mecanismo**: Activación de granulocitos en pulmones → cascada inflamatoria → lesión pulmonar y edema pulmonar no cardiogénico","guid":"uN5CEcLXHESf-zWcnTnAwA","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"- **Inicio**: Súbito; durante o hasta 6h post-transfusión","guid":"rlBQ89aTs_Mzbl4F7OwwJg","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"- **Manifestaciones**:","guid":"plZ36-LE26l5p87abMPzHA","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"- Características similares a SDRA","guid":"wHjUDqM8sihw1h8mTF3Dhg","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"- Signos de dificultad respiratoria","guid":"3EZpDo6ekmt7-KLJhAELFQ","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"- Signos de aumento de trabajo respiratorio","guid":"YShN8KW4FhDouf4NyDCTJA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"56","text":"- Fiebre, hipotensión","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"52","text":"- **Manejo**:","guid":"QsfNWky23ANm-oc7YsassQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"- Detener inmediatamente la transfusión","guid":"DisbM0F_09jZJRoyuHFn2w","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"- Soporte respiratorio (ventilación protectora)","guid":"amNByQyFN6pweH5FTniLeg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"- Soporte hemodinámico","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"8","text":"### Reacción Hemolítica\\NTransfusional Tardía\\N(DHTR)","guid":"W1423phdZaFbkHEXdzC01Q","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"- **Frecuencia**: 1:22, 000 transfusiones","guid":"HaBxKMotdUPmSPskpIrf5g","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"- **Mecanismo**: Respuesta anamnésica tardía a antígenos específicos de eritrocitos → hemólisis extravascular","guid":"YxWp5_xiBne8EDhfV48AAQ","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"- **Inicio**: Días o semanas post-transfusión","guid":"FAkP75M-X5O5IiEJosJU2Q","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"65","text":"- **Manifestaciones**:","guid":"Il0G7X-obMrWgmit4SE_jA","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"- Generalmente asintomática","guid":"dS1EsN5BTBFMo9NqWCWfdw","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"- Puede incluir fiebre leve, ictericia, anemia","guid":"mg-Ad9nSVqqFV0YigzEXFw","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"65","text":"- **Manejo**:","guid":"diB1_G7zuhEZyhICNoKAFA","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"- No requiere terapia aguda (autolimitada)","guid":"YnDsGrLBbjuqwfiEakm9NA","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"- Test de Coombs directo para prevenir futuras reacciones","guid":"8Ttr2MAbHfjyFkuOjIcZnQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"8","text":"### Púrpura\\NPostransfusional","guid":"4q7Ti2VUBO9Ip5cXznJ06Q","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"- **Frecuencia**: 1:57, 000 transfusiones","guid":"vfv07jIoIYxVk8LhyVFsRw","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"- **Mecanismo**: Respuesta anamnésica tardía a antígenos plaquetarios → destrucción de plaquetas","guid":"H360NdhvCl_iIEg8Zv-NNQ","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"- **Inicio**: 5-10 días post-transfusión","guid":"7B-F3Y0yaJ_YOfcSojcSBA","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"- **Manifestaciones**: Petequias, púrpura","guid":"cL2ljSMyz6fPuZPOErx5Gg","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"75","text":"- **Manejo**: Terapia con inmunoglobulina (IVIG)","guid":"gid2FaZC_cE4kpKoGo1BPA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"0","text":"## Complicaciones\\NTransfusionales No\\NInmunológicas","guid":"00KmVfJy1_QdYGcNSGoIBA","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"### Sepsis Asociada\\Na Transfusión","guid":"p9T86G58HrAGXU6Xhddx0Q","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"- **Frecuencia**: 1:10, 000-200,000 transfusiones","guid":"juwTbrLNr2E_CkOe-aNwYw","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"- **Mecanismo**: Contaminación bacteriana del producto sanguíneo","guid":"6b8YJs_RgXaHibJzCSkfrg","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"- **Inicio**: Dentro de 4h post-transfusión","guid":"gLgThEm-Xc1dfka_hII8yg","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"82","text":"- **Manifestaciones**: Fiebre, hipotensión, rigidez y otros signos de SIRS","guid":"71402BqQD4JyDWKDhEE1Qg","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"82","text":"- **Manejo**:","guid":"P_dwPYXNBCNmtQpTdhT_7Q","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"- Detener inmediatamente la transfusión","guid":"HI5JUxLfhVN4h05obORdOw","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"- Soporte hemodinámico inmediato","guid":"Rqn8tbObqUA6n0gFCUxx6Q","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"- Hemocultivos (paciente y producto sanguíneo)","guid":"7E22dqvYthVz-LZmsklU2Q","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"87","text":"- Antibióticos empíricos de amplio espectro","guid":"VFz76jmhaOjex31QfeTM0g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"81","text":"### Sobrecarga Circulatoria\\NAsociada a Transfusión (TACO)","guid":"TXShh2LI5y7WqF47DRHaLw","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"- **Frecuencia**: 1:9, 000 transfusiones","guid":"rNw0EokufvbYKvugpvaKxA","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"- **Mecanismo**: Sobrecarga de volumen","guid":"TDscYnXzwcb-kWeCuRyGDA","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"- **Inicio**: Durante o hasta 12h post-transfusión","guid":"OhiQHtJ3sOAFDvzyBnKmIQ","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"92","text":"- **Manifestaciones**: Signos de hipervolemia (disnea, galope S3, distensión venosa yugular, hipertensión)","guid":"YsYjsak8bpRV1LSBEo-jow","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"92","text":"- **Manejo**:","guid":"G6ggd_cKIwj1GtOEZdluWA","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"- Soporte respiratorio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"- Diuréticos para corregir estado de volumen","guid":"W-o1xbigubyXjxhSBQebeQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"81","text":"### Complicaciones Relacionadas\\Ncon Transfusión Masiva","guid":"YjcqcLCHy79_gTUnhZBWXQ","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"- **Hipocalcemia**: Por unión del calcio al citrato (anticoagulante)","guid":"0lWy7mVXxEuRGqT2xfL94w","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"- **Hiperpotasemia**: Por lisis de eritrocitos almacenados","guid":"JIPZQqDtPd3gcKkc7SGKCw","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"- **Hipotermia**: Por infusión rápida de productos sanguíneos fríos","guid":"V_zdCW9ouI4XeKeZPsAkzw","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"100","text":"- **Coagulopatía**: Multifactorial (dilución de plaquetas y factores, hipotermia, disfunción plaquetaria)","guid":"uCCO6iTiPWHMF64eZoAkLw","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"100","text":"- **Otros**:","guid":"O1yIscWrk720XqDG__aR1A","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"- Infecciones transmitidas por sangre (VIH, hepatitis B, hepatitis C)","guid":"R0GVDkTb4vdTD8MfV0M6iA","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"- Sobrecarga de hierro (hemocromatosis secundaria)","guid":"uoiWbV78oLG8Sxwsgx5Czw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"0","text":"## Manejo de Reacciones\\NTransfusionales Agudas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"### Principios\\NGenerales","guid":"nMY4tGvDyjzhc-zeacwpmw","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"- Reacción transfusional aguda: reacción adversa durante o hasta 24h post-transfusión","guid":"0nn-W-KRgy5SxSnKkc5pNw","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"- Todos los pacientes deben recibir evaluación y manejo inicial similar","guid":"gB7PXdiLiWTPBTQeKV0VSg","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"109","text":"- Sospechar en pacientes con cambios en signos vitales o nuevos síntomas","guid":"j9yKIl8PTZesY9qIzmKIRw","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"108","text":"### Pasos Iniciales\\Nde Manejo","guid":"yNBMpJ-be2ngIEr1T1B6dw","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"- **Todos los\\Npacientes**:","guid":"_-yo_AGSk2UGqx-JX4S2CQ","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"- Detener inmediatamente la transfusión","guid":"6kqB3Iw-6uRVwrI7wX-66g","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"- Mantener acceso IV con solución salina","guid":"dFktWX9QXLhGMVrp9xK0YA","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"114","text":"- Verificar compatibilidad de ID del paciente y producto","guid":"YKhP5VuveLUsadst7r5CzA","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"114","text":"- Realizar evaluación ABCDE y determinar gravedad","guid":"GoMRFaZKDg50syQl8hUzwg","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"114","text":"- Identificar causa subyacente","guid":"iKO7Z3U-No33qY1Hew7cOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"113","text":"- **Reacción\\Ngrave**:","guid":"qEpv9T6IsOuH2BjBgVcjTA","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"- Solicitar ayuda temprana (hematología, UCI)","guid":"RAcvJ659RzNVEuNUfreXUA","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"- Soporte respiratorio y hemodinámico","guid":"9rKwbumg-ukBrKVRnx3YCQ","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"120","text":"- Notificar al banco de sangre","guid":"fj3yazKadSFKVbvkQnsKAg","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"120","text":"- Iniciar tratamiento definitivo","guid":"56i-FFikITfxfZYJtOUBIA","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"113","text":"- **Reacción\\Nleve**:","guid":"WlqJPi9K9veXPBc7oSXI5Q","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"- Descartar manifestación temprana de reacción grave","guid":"SzS4eG_0ZOHDVr_153H_gw","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"- Alivio sintomático","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"- Reanudar si los síntomas se resuelven","guid":"p-lBXmxH3wiX48kUsQBmpA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"108","text":"### Evaluación\\Nde Gravedad","guid":"OKPCglMxJUK_9KdGW5XY7w","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"- **Leve**: Paciente estable con síntomas menores (fiebre aislada, reacción cutánea)","guid":"XKpPNuxnl2Z5aSKOAXtAdA","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"- **Grave**: Paciente inestable o con signos de dificultad respiratoria, shock, anafilaxia, hemólisis","guid":"RKGlJ5ZSoT8YwxGFr9TyBg","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"129","text":"- En caso de duda, tratar como grave","guid":"i2jTKColoVAktaV2lC-DCw","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"108","text":"###\\NInvestigaciones\\NIniciales","guid":"PaFzw9m-mc2yfQQToZnp_g","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"- Repetir tipificación ABO y pruebas cruzadas","guid":"HWHvMWCuzt-Cfq_NK2GItw","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"- Hemograma: evaluar anemia, trombocitopenia","guid":"EVKt9-oa8gkNz6BQamy2mg","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"- Evaluación de hemólisis","guid":"ww2K5JYntKtNO0KpE4cHxg","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"133","text":"- BMP: evaluar lesión renal aguda y desequilibrios electrolíticos","guid":"INdvEGGKWeZgQ_i-q1OC_A","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"133","text":"- Panel de coagulación: evaluar CID","guid":"h0_sIH68z6N10P9pFLnJLQ","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"133","text":"- Uroanálisis: evaluar hemoglobinuria","guid":"yIUXVwZziHe8DLLoRKWVjg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"0","text":"## Reacciones\\NTransfusionales\\NTardías","guid":"","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"- Ocurren >24 horas después de la transfusión (hasta semanas/meses)","guid":"QSIsUrNPprDBtGNYk7Z1ag","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"### Reacción Hemolítica\\NTransfusional Tardía\\N(DHTR)","guid":"r8u199hUn-mrMB0G-LEeWw","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"- **Frecuencia**: 1:22, 000 transfusiones","guid":"zW2Jc4v0LLGz1zl_g77CEg","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"- **Patofisiología**: Sensibilización previa a antígenos específicos de eritrocitos","guid":"2roIrEBcOlcffA3BcXTrJg","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"142","text":"- **Manifestaciones**: Generalmente asintomática; puede causar fiebre leve, ictericia, anemia","guid":"p-vErvcXryp-s0SKQVGp1g","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"142","text":"- **Diagnóstico**: DAT positivo, evaluación de anemia, evidencia de hemólisis","guid":"vzX8n_qQpQuVqsW7oR18Zw","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"142","text":"- **Tratamiento**: Generalmente autolimitada","guid":"hXJa5oUgsGqxlsj89PTVhQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"140","text":"### Púrpura\\NPostransfusional","guid":"kYIoTRA_X9Y5C9y9FVHUSw","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"- **Frecuencia**: 1:57,000 transfusiones (principalmente mujeres con antecedentes de múltiples embarazos/transfusiones)","guid":"hre90_XHD44CiwJawQO4Fg","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"- **Patofisiología**: Sensibilización previa a antígenos plaquetarios","guid":"P_q5Gg7zbjnEsrhO1o4ZPw","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"- **Manifestaciones**: Petequias, púrpura, trombocitopenia","guid":"WY-rSt7wQR07AkC47-cXTQ","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"148","text":"- **Diagnóstico**: Trombocitopenia grave, frotis sanguíneo normal, pruebas de coagulación normales","guid":"BjWywkxuhpwboDSrXdm0bA","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"148","text":"- **Tratamiento**: Inmunoglobulina intravenosa (IVIG), esteroides (eficacia no comprobada)","guid":"AKyAh9tPl89B5faJDXQOgQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"154","parent":"140","text":"### Enfermedad Injerto Contra\\NHuésped Asociada a Transfusión","guid":"epPMrKb3tDPW21TdH6fznw","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"- Complicación extremadamente rara en pacientes gravemente inmunocomprometidos","guid":"mo1Fpu1wlHQGkiJEgcba3Q","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"154","text":"- Manifestaciones: Erupción maculopapular, fiebre, diarrea, fallo medular 5-10 días post-transfusión","guid":"OdN16eC9HkUspl0kh_aAdw","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"154","text":"- Casi siempre fatal","guid":"9k5yqwPqq8FOnsgkdA41jA","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":157,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Hematología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Hematología","filename":"AMBOSS Reacción Transfusional-2025","id":"map_1042","resolved_references":[]}